276
00:18:13,275 --> 00:18:16,445
<i>Aku bisa ke sana bila kau mau</i>

277
00:18:16,529 --> 00:18:19,907
<i>Aku akan berlari dan terbang kepadamu</i>

278
00:18:19,990 --> 00:18:23,244
<i>Akan kupeluk kau dan kuberi semua untukmu</i>

279
00:18:27,122 --> 00:18:28,749
