aku tetap mendukungmu.

436
00:29:20,192 --> 00:29:23,737
Tunggu, Yi-seo. Kau mau ke mana
tanpa transportasi umum?

437
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:24,946
Aku naik taksi.

438
00:29:25,071 --> 00:29:27,073
Tak ada taksi di Itaewon. Kau tahu, 'kan?

439
00:29:27,741 --> 00:29:29,951
Aku temani kau sampai bus pertama.

440
00:29:30,035 --> 00:29:30,911
Ayo main lagi.

441
00:29:31,786 --> 00:29:33,955
Ada jalan besar kalau aku lewat sini.

442
00:29:34,039 --> 00:29:35,582
Aku bisa dapat taksi di sana.

443
00:29:36,708 --> 00:29:38,168
Kenapa kau tiba-tiba pergi?

444
00:29:38,668 --> 00:29:40,128
Apa karena kau tak suka aku?

445
00:29:43,298 --> 00:29:44,424
Ya.

446
00:29:45,425 --> 00:29:46,301
Kenapa?

447
00:29:46,843 --> 00:29:48,512
Kenapa kau tak suka denganku?

448
00:29:49,846 --> 00:29:52,849
Wajah, cara bicara, suaramu.

449
00:29:52,933 --> 00:29:55,602
Bola mata, gigimu, bulu matamu,

450
00:29:55,685 --> 00:29:57,270
