778
00:53:21,715 --> 00:53:23,133
<i>Dan aku tak bisa</i>

779
00:53:25,385 --> 00:53:27,095
<i>menahan dorongan ini.</i>

780
00:53:28,388 --> 00:53:30,974
Apa mungkin kau menyukai Sae-ro-yi?

781
00:53:42,778 --> 00:53:44,112
<i>Aku menyukainya.</i>

